This also allows to reuse this thread-pool if needed for other stuff, like parallel CSS parsing (#22478), and to share more code with Gecko, which is always nice.  This cherry-picks https://github.com/servo/servo/pull/22487, with a few minor fixes to the build that are landing as part of the sync associated to this bug, and an lsan exception tweak to point to the right module since it's moving.
